OL,3,CReeves' enormous budget should perhaps
OL,4,Chave been bigger still
OL,6,FMaybe. But there is a case to be made
OL,7,Fthat Reeves could and should have been
OL,8,Fmore ambitious, or at least more
OL,9,Fcreative, notably on taxing and
OL,10,Fspending.
OL,12,FFirst of all, lots of important public
OL,13,Fservices will still feel desperately
OL,14,Fsqueezed, because the lion's share of
OL,15,Fa rise in resources is going to
OL,16,Fhealth, education and defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
