OL,3,CReeves' enormous budget should perhaps
OL,4,Chave been bigger still
OL,6,FFourth, what the OBR says is one of
OL,7,Fthe most significant fiscal
OL,8,Floosening's of modern times will
OL,9,Falmost certainly mean interest rates
OL,10,Fwill be higher for longer - which is a
OL,11,Fpain for private-sector borrowers and
OL,12,Ffor the highly indebted government
OL,13,Fitself.
OL,15,FSo although I know it sounds mad, on
OL,16,Fthe logic of what Reeves says she
OL,17,Fwants to do - namely revive the public
OL,18,Fsector and increase investment - she
OL,19,Fshould actually have raised taxes by
OL,20,Fmore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
