OL,3,CReeves' enormous budget should perhaps
OL,4,Chave been bigger still
OL,6,FHer failure to put up fuel duties -
OL,7,Fwhich haven't been increased since
OL,8,F2010 - looks particularly eccentric,
OL,9,Fand indeed self-damaging, at this
OL,10,Fcritical juncture.
OL,12,FThe point is that increasing
OL,13,Femployers' national insurance will
OL,14,Fnever raise the headline #25bn a year,
OL,15,Faccording to the OBR, because
OL,16,Fbusinesses will respond to it by
OL,17,Fcutting staff wages and reducing
OL,18,Femployment. So the net yield in five
OL,19,Fyears will be nearer #15bn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
